Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.20,0:00:10.17,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{There.}Xong.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.17,0:00:12.53,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{That does it for the big cleanup.}Vậy là tổng vệ sinh đã xong.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.92,0:00:18.62,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{It went really quickly thanks to the \Nyoung master's and Natsume's help.}Nhờ chủ nhân và Natsume giúp đỡ nên xong nhanh ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.39,0:00:21.61,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I know.}Phải rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:21.61,0:00:26.29,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I should prepare tea before \Nthey get home from shopping.}Chuẩn bị trà để chờ họ đi mua sắm về nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.51,0:00:46.84,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Yes, who is it?}Vâng, ai vậy ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.88,0:00:51.80,Main,Master,0,0,0,,{Hey.}Chào.
