Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.33,0:01:12.34,Show_Title - Sus Maid,,0,0,0,,{\fad(3175,0)}{The }{\fs40\c&H953CA0&}{Maid }{\c\fs}{I Hired Recently\NIs }{\fs40\c&H953CA0&}{Mysterious}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.67,0:02:39.55,Ep_Title - Sus Maid,Text,0,0,0,,{\fad(500,500)\blur2\an2\fsp.5\q2\pos(387,300)}{Episode 11:     }{\fsp3}{It Must Have Always Been...}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.88,0:02:36.95,Top,Natsume,0,0,0,,{So heavy...}Nặng quá...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.44,0:02:41.48,Top,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Why did Lilith ask us to buy so much stuff?}Tại sao Lilith mua lắm đồ thế...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:41.48,0:02:42.92,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{What are you complaining about?}Phàn nàn gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.15,0:02:47.42,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{You're the one who said you wanted to go \Nshopping because you didn't want to clean.}Cô là người nói dọn dẹp\N phiền phức nên muốn đi mua đồ còn gì.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.20,0:02:53.85,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{By the way...}Cơ mà...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.81,0:02:56.80,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Th-Thanks.}C-cảm ơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.03,0:03:01.05,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{I'm glad I came here.}Tôi vui khi đến đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.05,0:03:03.69,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{I got to see Lilith doing well...}Gặp được Lilith khoẻ mạnh...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.69,0:03:10.65,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{A-And thanks to you, I finally \Ngot to tell Lilith how I feel.}V-Và nhờ cậu mà tôi có thể truyền đạt cảm xúc cho Lilith...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.89,0:03:13.82,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{You just told her what you wanted to tell her.}Cô chỉ nói những gì mình muốn nói thôi mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.82,0:03:15.61,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I didn't do anything.}Tôi có làm gì đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.61,0:03:17.17,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{You did!}Có đó!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.30,0:03:23.04,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{I always thought it was embarrassing \Nto tell someone how you feel.}Tôi đã nghĩ thật xấu hổ khi nói ra cảm xúc bản thân.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.04,0:03:25.33,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{So it was a shock to me.}Thế nên tôi đã rất sốc.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.49,0:03:34.36,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Once I get back to my mansion, I'm going to \Ntell the person I love that I love them.}Khi quay lại dinh thự, tôi sẽ nói với người tôi yêu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.36,0:03:37.77,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{I realized it's important \Nto tell them properly.}Tôi đã hiểu việc nói rõ ra là rất quan trọng.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.77,0:03:41.53,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{What? I thought you loved Lilith.}Ủa? Tưởng cô thích Lilith?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.53,0:03:42.17,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Huh?!}Hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.17,0:03:44.65,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{I mean, I-I do, but...}À thì có nhưng...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.65,0:03:51.87,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{The love I have for Lilith isn't the \Nsame as the love I have for my master.}Tình cảm tôi dành cho Lilith \Nkhông giống với dành cho chủ nhân...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.10,0:03:53.49,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Oh, I get it.}Hiểu rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.49,0:03:56.31,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{You love your master.}Cô yêu chủ nhân à.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.41,0:03:58.56,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Am I wrong?}Tôi sai à?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.56,0:04:00.69,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,Không sai nhưng...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.13,0:04:04.53,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,Thích cũng có nhiều kiểu lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.36,0:04:09.68,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Like, love for your family, \Nlove for your friends...}Như là tình yêu gia đình, yêu bè bạn...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.38,0:04:13.88,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{A kid like you wouldn't understand.}Trẻ con sẽ không hiểu đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.76,0:04:17.24,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{A-Anyway, it's getting cold.}C-Cơ mà trời sắp lạnh lên rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.24,0:04:18.55,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Let's hurry home.}Mau về nhà thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.25,0:04:24.49,Main,Master,0,0,0,,{Thanks.}Cảm ơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.42,0:04:31.09,Main,Master,0,0,0,,{You don't need to be so tense.}Không cần lo lắng đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.09,0:04:34.33,Main,Master,0,0,0,,{I just came to see how you're \Ndoing, since I was in the area.}Tôi chỉ tiện đường ghé qua thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.33,0:04:35.10,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Okay.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.45,0:04:39.62,Main,Master,0,0,0,,{I'm sorry you had to take \Ncare of Natsume, too.}Xin lỗi vì để cô phải lo cho Natsume nữa nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.62,0:04:40.86,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Oh, no.}Không ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.86,0:04:42.62,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{It's not a problem.}Không có vấn đề gì.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.18,0:04:44.36,Main,Master,0,0,0,,{Where is Natsume?}Natsume đâu?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.36,0:04:47.35,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{She's out shopping right now.}Đi mua sắm rồi ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.35,0:04:48.98,Main,Master,0,0,0,,{I see.}Vậy à.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.98,0:04:50.85,Main,Master,0,0,0,,{Is she assisting you well?}Con bé có phụ giúp đàng hoàng không?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.07,0:04:51.95,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Yes.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.95,0:04:53.91,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{She's been a great help.}Rất có ích.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.91,0:04:55.93,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{With cleaning, with laundry...}Lau dọn, giặt giũ...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.97,0:04:59.04,Main,Master,0,0,0,,{I'm glad to hear it.}Vậy thì tốt.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.66,0:05:07.73,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Um, master...}Chủ nhân...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.83,0:05:15.97,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I'm very sorry for causing trouble for others \Nat the mansion due to my own selfishness.}Tôi xin lỗi vì sự ích kỉ \Ncủa bản thân đã làm phiền đến mọi người.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.50,0:05:20.87,Main,Master,0,0,0,,{Don't worry about that anymore.}Đừng bận tâm nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.39,0:05:23.57,Main,Master,0,0,0,,{Everyone understands.}Ai cũng hiểu mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.14,0:05:28.14,Main,Master,0,0,0,,{This is a nice mansion.}Dinh thự tuyệt nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.14,0:05:28.93,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Yes.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.93,0:05:32.45,Main,Master,0,0,0,,{And it's well-maintained.}Và được chăm sóc rất kĩ.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.52,0:05:35.26,Main,Master,0,0,0,,{You do all this by yourself?}Cô tự mình làm hết hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.26,0:05:36.96,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Yes.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.96,0:05:39.31,Main,Master,0,0,0,,{That's impressive.}Tuyệt thật.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.31,0:05:44.59,Main,Master,0,0,0,,{I can see that you truly care about \Nthis mansion, and about your master.}Cô thực sự quan tâm đến chủ nhân của dinh thự này nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.64,0:05:51.47,Main,Master,0,0,0,,{Does it have to do with your past?}Quả nhiên có liên quan đến quá khứ nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.48,0:06:03.92,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{When I was little, my parents disappeared, \Nand I was left without a home.}Khi còn nhỏ, ba mẹ tôi biến mất và tôi đã mất đi nơi ở.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.92,0:06:07.88,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I was passed around between \Nrelatives and acquaintances.}Tôi lưu lạc giữa những người họ hàng.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.94,0:06:17.21,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{No one wanted to give me a home until...}Không ai đưa tay ra giúp đỡ...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.87,0:06:23.14,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{The young master's parents, who were \Nclose friends with mine, took me in.}Ba mẹ của chủ nhân, những\N người bạn thân của ba mẹ tôi, đã đưa tay ra.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.32,0:06:32.27,Flashback - Sus Maid,Yuuri's Mom,0,0,0,,{Here.}Đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.94,0:06:36.34,Flashback - Sus Maid,Yuuri's Mom,0,0,0,,{It's herbal tea.}Trà thảo mộc đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.34,0:06:38.49,Flashback - Sus Maid,Yuuri's Mom,0,0,0,,{I hope you like it.}Hi vọng cháu thích nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.64,0:06:44.59,Flashback - Sus Maid,Yuuri's Mom,0,0,0,,{Go ahead.}Xin mời.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.59,0:06:56.17,Flashback - Sus Maid,Yuuri's Mom,0,0,0,,{I can make you a late-night \Nsnack if you're hungry.}Nếu đói tôi có thể làm món ăn đêm.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.28,0:07:00.16,Flashback - Sus Maid,Yuuri's Dad,0,0,0,,{You don't have to hold back.}Không cần ngại đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.28,0:07:07.28,Flashback - Sus Maid,Yuuri's Dad,0,0,0,,{Lilith-kun, I know the agreement was that \Nwe would take care of you for half a year.}Lilith, bọn chú đã nhận chăm sóc cháu nửa năm.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.53,0:07:12.89,Flashback - Sus Maid,Yuuri's Dad,0,0,0,,{But you're welcome to stay as long as you'd like.}Nhưng cứ ở đây đến khi nào thấy chán.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.78,0:07:16.73,Flashback - Sus Maid,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Wh-Why?}T-Tại sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.03,0:07:21.80,Flashback - Sus Maid,Yuuri's Dad,0,0,0,,{It's partly because of our \Ngratitude toward your parents,}Vì bọn chú được ba mẹ cháu giúp đỡ rất nhiều,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.80,0:07:24.84,Flashback - Sus Maid,Yuuri's Dad,0,0,0,,{but most of all, it's because \Nwe don't want to abandon you.}nhưng hơn cả là vì không thể bỏ rơi cháu.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.84,0:07:26.16,Flashback - Sus Maid,Yuuri's Dad,0,0,0,,{Is that not a good reason?}Vậy đủ chưa?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.97,0:07:39.87,Flashback - Sus Maid,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Who are you?}Chị là ai?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.24,0:07:46.98,Flashback - Sus Maid,Lilith,0,0,0,,{U-Um...}À ừm...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.05,0:07:53.48,Flashback - Sus Maid,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{What's wrong?}Sao thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.71,0:07:55.70,Flashback - Sus Maid,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Why are you hiding your eyes?}Sao lại giấu mắt đi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.70,0:07:59.12,Flashback - Sus Maid,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Because my eyes are creepy...}Vì mắt chị đáng sợ lắm...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.67,0:08:04.40,Flashback - Sus Maid,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{No, they're not.}Không, không phải.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.31,0:08:06.60,Flashback - Sus Maid,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{They're pretty.}Chúng đẹp lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.11,0:08:10.75,Flashback - Sus Maid,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Your eyes sparkle like the stars.}Lấp lánh như những ngôi sao.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.75,0:08:11.95,Flashback - Sus Maid,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{They're really pretty.}Chúng thật đẹp.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.23,0:08:26.42,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{The people of this mansion \Nwelcomed me like real family.}Những người ở dinh thự này xem tôi như người nhà.
