Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.47,0:08:29.93,Main,Text,0,0,0,,{\fad(475,0)\fnTimes New Roman\c&H000000&\3c&HFFFFFF&\fs20\shad0\frx30\an5\fax.4\bord1\3a&H20&\fay-.005\frz210.3\pos(238.667,102.667)}{Recruiting Its 53rd Class}
Dialogue: 1,0:08:27.74,0:08:35.50,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{About a year in, I decided I wanted to \Ngo to a boarding school for servants.}Sau 1 năm, tôi quyết định vào học viện đào tạo người hầu.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.16,0:08:42.79,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{They were worried, but they understood \Nmy wish, and allowed me to study there.}Họ khá lo lắng nhưng vẫn tôn trọng mong muốn của tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.28,0:08:48.67,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I studied my hardest, \Nvowing to repay them someday.}Tôi học tập chăm chỉ để có thể trả ơn họ.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.81,0:08:55.18,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{After I graduated, I was set \Nto work at your mansion.}Sau khi tốt nghiệp, tôi đã được phân vào\N làm hầu gái nhà chủ nhân.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.27,0:08:58.65,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{And...}Và...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.65,0:09:00.62,Flashback - Sus Maid,Lilith,0,0,0,,{N-No...}K-Không thể nào...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.62,0:09:05.84,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{That's when I received the news that the \Nyoung master's parents had died in an accident.}Lúc đó, tôi nghe tin ba mẹ chủ nhân đã qua đời do tai nạn.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.05,0:09:12.40,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I saw him in the same light as I saw \Nmyself when I lost my parents.}Tôi đã cảm thấy chủ nhân sẽ giống như tôi lúc đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.78,0:09:25.28,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{It was my turn to protect him.}Lần này tôi sẽ bảo vệ chủ nhân.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.92,0:09:27.61,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Along with this mansion.}Cùng với dinh thự này.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.66,0:09:35.03,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{We're home.}Bọn tôi về rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.03,0:09:36.93,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{We finally made it.}Cuối cùng cũng về đến.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.87,0:09:41.01,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Hey, listen to this, Lilith.}Nè Lilith.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.01,0:09:42.17,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Natsume's...}Natsume...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.37,0:09:48.71,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Would you go inside already? \NThis stuff's heavy.}Này, mau vào nhà đi. Nặng lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.52,0:09:53.04,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Welcome home, young master, Natsume.}Chào mừng hai người, chủ nhân, Natsume.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.04,0:09:55.64,Main,Master,0,0,0,,{Natsume, mind your tone.}Natsume, ăn nói đàng hoàng vào.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.64,0:09:58.18,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Wh-Why are you here?}T-Tại sao ngài lại ở đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.98,0:10:01.75,Main,Master,0,0,0,,{Because you weren't coming home.}Vì cô không trở về.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.75,0:10:03.40,Main,Master,0,0,0,,{I was worried.}Nên tôi lo lắng.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.63,0:10:06.62,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Y-You didn't have to come get me.}N-Ngài không cần đến đón đâu.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.02,0:10:10.62,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{I was about to come home soon anyway.}Tôi định sẽ về sớm thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.74,0:10:16.12,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Lilith, who's this?}Lilith, ai đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.35,0:10:21.67,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{This man is the master of the \NmansiVânon that I worked at previously.}Vâng, là chủ nhân của dinh thự tôi làm hồi trước.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.10,0:10:24.13,Main,Master,0,0,0,,{Nice to meet you, Yuuri-kun.}Rất vui được gặp cậu, Yuuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.13,0:10:26.57,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{N-Nice to meet you.}R-Rất vui được gặp.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.44,0:10:28.69,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Why...}Tại sao...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.70,0:10:32.60,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Young master?}Chủ nhân?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.16,0:10:34.98,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Lilith is my maid!}Lilith là hầu gái của tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.98,0:10:36.76,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I'm not letting anyone take her!}Tôi không để ai đưa cô ấy đi đâu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.76,0:10:37.73,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Young master...}Chủ nhân...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.10,0:10:46.40,Main,Master,0,0,0,,{It's all right, Yuuri-kun.}Không sao đâu Yuuri.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.75,0:10:48.72,Main,Master,0,0,0,,{I'm not going to take her back with me.}Tôi không đến dẫn cô ấy về.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.72,0:10:49.85,Main,Master,0,0,0,,{Don't worry.}Nên đừng lo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.85,0:10:51.71,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{R-Really?}T-Thật sao?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.71,0:10:52.60,Main,Master,0,0,0,,{Yes.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.27,0:10:59.70,Main,Master,0,0,0,,{Well, I'd better get going.}Giờ thì về thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.30,0:11:05.73,Main,Master,0,0,0,,{Natsume, get ready, please.}Natsume, chuẩn bị đi.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.73,0:11:06.81,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Fine.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.39,0:11:15.92,Main,Master,0,0,0,,{Thanks for taking care \Nof Natsume, Yuuri-kun.}Cảm ơn vì đã chăm sóc Natsume nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.92,0:11:17.36,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Not at all.}Không có gì.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.36,0:11:20.23,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{I was the one who took care of him.}Tôi mới là người chăm sóc cậu ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.23,0:11:22.42,Main,Master,0,0,0,,{Now, now, Natsume.}Thôi nào Natsume.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.40,0:11:28.45,Main,Master,0,0,0,,{Also, please be good to \NLilith going forward, too.}Và xin hãy lo cho Lilith nữa nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.67,0:11:35.74,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I will.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.59,0:11:39.79,Main,Master,0,0,0,,{Well, then...}Vậy thì...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.79,0:11:40.97,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Master...}Chủ nhân...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.57,0:11:47.37,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Thank you.}Cảm ơn ngài.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.17,0:11:51.63,Main,Master,0,0,0,,{May we come visit again sometime?}Lần sau bọn tôi đến chơi được chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.63,0:11:54.45,Main,Master,0,0,0,,{I'm sure Natsume will be missing you, too.}Natsume sẽ nhớ hai người lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.45,0:11:55.68,Main,Natsume,0,0,0,,{Hey!}Này!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.45,0:11:57.37,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Yes.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.37,0:11:59.65,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Is that all right, young master?}Được chứ ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.65,0:12:00.41,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Yeah.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.14,0:12:02.87,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Please come whenever you'd like.}Cứ đến khi nào muốn.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.07,0:12:04.20,Main,Master,0,0,0,,{Thank you.}Cảm ơn nhé.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.66,0:12:12.35,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{They're gone.}Họ về rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.72,0:12:13.60,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Yeah.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.91,0:12:17.51,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Wh-What? What's wrong?}C-Cái gì? Sao thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.51,0:12:21.82,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I made dinner for three.}Tôi lỡ làm đồ ăn cho 3 người rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.19,0:12:24.62,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,Tưởng gì.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.62,0:12:26.48,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{What shall I do?}Sao giờ ta?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.48,0:12:27.89,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,Tôi sẽ ăn hết.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.89,0:12:31.62,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I can eat as much of your \Ndelicious cooking as you make.}Tài nấu ăn của Lilith thì ăn cỡ nào chả được.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.67,0:12:41.84,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{It's kind of quiet, isn't it, young master?}Cảm giác yên tĩnh nhỉ, chủ nhân?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.84,0:12:42.76,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Yeah.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.49,0:12:49.64,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,Không ngờ Natsume đi rồi lại yên tĩnh đến thế.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.64,0:12:51.92,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Yeah, it is.}Phải nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.81,0:13:00.81,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{It hasn't been just the \Ntwo of us for a while.}Đã lâu rồi mới chỉ có 2 ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.81,0:13:02.55,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Kind of exciting, isn't it?}Cảm giác thật hồi hộp nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.55,0:13:03.29,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Yeah.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.74,0:13:11.71,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Young master, would you like some more?}Chủ nhân, ngài ăn nữa chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.07,0:13:13.83,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Yeah. Please.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.46,0:13:21.89,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{It's been too long since it's \Nbeen just the two of us.}Lâu rồi mới có 2 người ở riêng.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.89,0:13:24.01,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I've forgotten how to converse properly.}Mình quên mất cách nói chuyện luôn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.21,0:13:31.65,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{But there's so much I need to tell him...}Nhưng mình có nhiều chuyện muốn nói lắm...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.51,0:13:38.97,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Here you go.}Của ngài đây.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.59,0:13:40.78,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Thanks.}Cảm ơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.64,0:13:43.00,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Young master...}Chủ nhân...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.00,0:13:46.26,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Would you like to go out tomorrow?}Ngày mai chúng ta ra ngoài chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.43,0:13:52.94,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I just realized we hadn't \Ngone out together yet.}Tôi nhận ra mình chưa từng đi riêng với chủ nhân lần nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.19,0:13:57.69,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Y-You mean a date?!}Y-Ý cô là hẹn hò hả?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.69,0:13:58.76,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Da—}H-Hẹn--
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.76,0:14:00.68,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Um...}Chuyện này...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.13,0:14:03.39,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Yes, a date.}Vâng, là hẹn hò.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.63,0:14:04.65,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{All right.}Hiểu rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.65,0:14:06.24,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{We're going on a date tomorrow!}Ngày mai chúng ta sẽ hẹn hò nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.77,0:14:16.57,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{It's gotten so cold.}Trời bắt đầu lạnh rồi nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.57,0:14:17.55,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Yeah.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.55,0:14:20.53,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Are you not cold, young master?}Ngài có lạnh không?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.53,0:14:22.19,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Not at all.}Không hẳn.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.19,0:14:24.45,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Especially since you gave me this.}Cô tặng tôi thứ này mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.69,0:14:32.44,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Is something the matter?}Có chuyện gì sao ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.44,0:14:33.65,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Your clothes...}Quần áo...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.37,0:14:37.96,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I dressed up the best I could.}Tôi đã mặc thật đẹp đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.96,0:14:40.74,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{It's my first date with you, after all.}Dù gì cũng là ngày hẹn hò đầu tiên mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.15,0:14:42.23,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Just kidding.}Đùa thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.23,0:14:43.20,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Yeah.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.20,0:14:44.63,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{You look beautiful.}Đẹp lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.10,0:14:48.22,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Thank you.}C-Cảm ơn ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.53,0:14:52.35,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Where shall we go, young master?}Chúng ta đi đâu đây?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.35,0:14:54.35,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Let's see...}Phải nhỉ...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.35,0:14:57.46,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I'd like to go wherever you'd like to.}Hay đi mấy chỗ chủ nhân thích.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.46,0:14:58.87,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{We can go anywhere.}Đi đâu cũng được.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.72,0:15:01.20,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{But...}Nhưng...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.43,0:15:04.62,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Anything is fun if I'm with you.}Miễn có cô là được.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.46,0:15:11.12,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Wh-Why don't we stop by \Na café for some hot cocoa?}V-Vậy chúng ta vào quán cafe uống cacao nhé?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.63,0:15:13.44,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Yeah, good idea.}Ừm, vậy đi,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.44,0:15:15.59,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Shall we, then?}Chúng ta đi thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.50,0:15:24.83,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{What's the matter, young lady?}Có chuyện gì vậy tiểu thư?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.83,0:15:28.91,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Why do I have so many lessons \Nwhen it's the holiday season?}Tại sao cuối năm mà tôi phải học nhiều thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.91,0:15:30.74,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{You just have to get through today.}Chỉ hết hôm nay thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.74,0:15:34.00,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{And then you're going on vacation \Noverseas with your parents.}Từ mai là tiểu thư đi du lịch nước ngoài rồi còn gì.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.33,0:15:38.70,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Yuuri-san?!}Yuuri?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.70,0:15:41.02,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Hey, Fujisaki, look at that.}Nhìn kìa Fujisaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.02,0:15:42.46,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Do you think...}Không có lẽ...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.46,0:15:44.01,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{That's a d-date, isn't it?}Họ đang hẹn hò?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.01,0:15:45.45,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{It is, isn't it?!}Chắc thế rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.45,0:15:47.67,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{No, I'm pretty sure they're just shopping.}Không, chỉ là đi mua sắm thôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.67,0:15:49.74,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{What are you talking about?!}Họ đang nói gì thế?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.74,0:15:50.75,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Look at them!}Nhìn họ xem!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.75,0:15:52.51,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{They're having so much fun!}Có vẻ vui lắm.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.79,0:15:54.39,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{We can't just sit here.}Không thể ngồi yên được.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.39,0:15:56.83,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{Let's follow them, Fujisaki.}Bám theo thôi, Fujisaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.83,0:15:57.86,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{We will not.}Không được.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.86,0:15:59.87,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{You have piano lessons.}Chúng ta còn giờ học piano.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.87,0:16:01.91,Main,Tsukasa,0,0,0,,{I don't care about—}Tôi không quan tâm--
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.81,0:16:02.39,Main,Fujisaki,0,0,0,,{Young lady.}Tiểu thư.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.67,0:16:17.15,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{It warms you up, huh?}Ấm lên rồi nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.12,0:16:19.96,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Yeah.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.25,0:16:25.42,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{It looks like it might snow \Nif it gets any colder.}Có vẻ tuyết sẽ rơi nếu lạnh hơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.42,0:16:26.95,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Snow, huh?}Tuyết à?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.28,0:16:32.67,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Hey, Lilith...}Nè Lilith...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.67,0:16:33.44,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Yes?}Vâng?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.05,0:16:37.26,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{There's somewhere I want to go after this.}Có nơi tôi muốn đến.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.26,0:16:38.30,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Is that all right?}Được chứ?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.87,0:16:41.10,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Yes, of course.}Vâng, được ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.30,0:16:45.24,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{So where is it that you'd like to go?}Vậy chúng ta sẽ đi đâu ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.42,0:17:07.90,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I was afraid to come here by myself.}Tôi sợ phải đến đây một mình.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.63,0:17:09.69,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Young master...}Chủ nhân...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.17,0:17:12.84,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{But now, with you here, \NI could finally do it.}Nhưng nhờ có cô, tôi đã đến được.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:12.84,0:17:13.83,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Thanks.}Cảm ơn.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.50,0:17:19.68,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Mom and Dad are doing well \Ntogether in Heaven, right?}Ba mẹ hẳn đang mạnh khoẻ trên thiên đường nhỉ?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.11,0:17:22.01,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Yes, of course.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.49,0:17:26.53,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{The two of them are watching over you.}Bọn họ đang dõi theo chủ nhân đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.74,0:17:30.45,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Yeah.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.26,0:17:33.70,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{You're right.}Phải nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.46,0:17:37.08,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Don't worry.}Đừng lo lắng.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.46,0:17:40.32,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I have Lilith. I'm all right.}Con đã có Lilith bên cạnh.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.70,0:17:43.91,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Well, I'll be back again.}Vậy con sẽ quay lại sau.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.39,0:17:52.78,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Master, Madam, it's been a while.}Chủ nhân, phu nhân, đã lâu không gặp.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.78,0:17:53.83,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{It's Lilith.}Là Lilith ạ.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.49,0:17:56.95,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Don't worry about the young master.}Xin hãy an tâm về chủ nhân.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.95,0:18:00.03,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I'll take care of him.}Tôi sẽ chăm sóc ngài ấy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.42,0:18:01.47,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,Lilith?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.47,0:18:03.70,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Yes, I'm coming.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.92,0:18:15.53,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{It's so pretty.}Đẹp quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.01,0:18:17.09,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Yeah.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.33,0:18:26.19,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Is something the matter?}Có chuyện gì sao ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.85,0:18:30.16,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{You looked so pretty, gazing at the lights.}Trông cô đẹp quá, y như trình diễn ánh sáng vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.16,0:18:31.82,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I couldn't help but gaze at you.}Tôi không thể rời mắt.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.29,0:18:37.64,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I-I'm sorry for having all the fun.}X-Xin lỗi vì chỉ mình tôi tận hưởng.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.64,0:18:39.21,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Not at all.}Không sao.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.21,0:18:40.71,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I'm having fun, too.}Tôi cũng đang vui vẻ mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.10,0:18:46.25,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Besides, it's been a long time \Nsince I've had you to myself.}Với cả đã lâu rồi tôi mới đi riêng với cô.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.60,0:18:50.18,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I-I'm always your maid.}T-Tôi lúc nào cũng là hầu gái của chủ nhân mà.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:50.50,0:18:53.16,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{You were busy with Natsume \Nuntil just recently.}Nhưng lúc trước toàn bận rộn với Natsume.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.16,0:18:55.90,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{You had no time for me.}Nên đâu có thời gian dành cho tôi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.90,0:18:58.27,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Th-That's right.}P-Phải rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.85,0:19:04.73,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{So I realized we have to cherish \Nthe time we have together more.}Thế nên tôi muốn trân trọng\N khoảng thời gian của riêng hai ta.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.54,0:19:10.58,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Because I love you, Lilith.}Vì tôi yêu cô, Lilith.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.60,0:19:28.23,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{There's something I've been \Nwondering this whole time...}Tôi đã luôn tò mò...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.51,0:19:33.34,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{What kind of "love" do you mean \Nwhen you say you love me?}Với chủ nhân thì yêu là gì?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.53,0:19:41.91,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I don't know.}Tôi không biết.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.79,0:19:48.10,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{But I want to find out \Ngoing forward, with you.}Nhưng tôi muốn cùng cô tìm ra nó.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.86,0:19:59.77,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Remember when you asked me if I was only \Nby your side because you're my master?}Ngài còn nhớ lần hỏi tôi rằng tôi\N đến bên ngài chỉ vì đó là chủ nhân của mình không?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.77,0:20:00.54,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Yeah.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.13,0:20:09.21,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{When I'm with you, I feel so happy \Nthat my face turns beet red.}Lúc ở cùng chủ nhân, mặt tôi ửng đỏ và rất hạnh phúc.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.48,0:20:11.65,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{And my chest warms up.}Ngực thì nóng lên.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.18,0:20:17.22,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I want to be by your side not because \Nyou're my master, but because you're you.}Tôi bên cạnh ngài không\N chỉ vì là chủ nhân mình, mà vì ngài là ngài.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.96,0:20:22.59,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I don't know yet if I can \Nrespond to your love.}Tôi vẫn chưa thể đáp lại tình yêu của chủ nhân.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.07,0:20:25.94,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{But I adore you all the same.}Nhưng tôi cũng sẽ cố gắng.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.70,0:20:30.76,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Thanks!}Cảm ơn!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.42,0:20:40.62,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{It must have always been \Nthat way, ever since back then.}Nhất định từ ngày đó, mình đã luôn...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.57,0:20:53.58,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{And from now on, too.}Và từ giờ cũng vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.12,0:21:00.44,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I hope you continue to love me, \Neven after you know everything about me.}Mình hi vọng ngài ấy sẽ tiếp tục yêu mình.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.09,0:21:07.35,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Well, the snow is getting heavier.}Tuyết rơi nặng hạt rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.35,0:21:09.30,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Let's go home, young master.}Chúng ta về nhà thôi, chủ nhân.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.30,0:21:10.35,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{You're right.}Phải nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.58,0:21:15.19,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{For now, that's all I want to wish for.}Đó là những gì mình mong muốn.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.79,0:21:26.87,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{It's really piled up.}Đầy tuyết luôn.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.09,0:21:29.27,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I know.}Phải rồi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.27,0:21:32.68,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I'm going to make a snowman \Nto surprise Lilith.}Làm người tuyết cho Lilith hết hồn nào.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.43,0:21:40.15,Italics,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Oh, she already made one.}Cô ấy làm rồi à?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.98,0:21:49.22,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Young master?}Chủ nhân?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.23,0:21:55.46,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{My.}Chà.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.46,0:21:58.26,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{You made a snowman, too.}Chủ nhân cũng làm người tuyết ạ?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.26,0:21:59.13,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Yeah.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.48,0:22:00.24,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Huh?}Ủa?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.54,0:22:03.05,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{That one...}Con này...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.32,0:22:08.89,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{They're so cute next to each other.}Chúng dễ thương ghê.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.89,0:22:12.15,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{They look just like you and me.}Y như tôi và chủ nhân vậy.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:12.15,0:22:13.04,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Yeah.}Ừm.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.04,0:22:14.36,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Aren't they cute?}Dễ thương không?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.53,0:22:17.59,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{I'm going to make kids for them, too.}Giờ tôi sẽ làm con cho chúng nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.59,0:22:19.04,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{K-Kids?!}C-Con cái?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.04,0:22:20.92,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Lots of them!}Đẻ nhiều luôn!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.61,0:22:23.92,Italics,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Lots?!}Nhiều?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.82,0:22:29.25,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{They're cute.}Dễ thương quá.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.14,0:22:33.11,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,Ngài lạnh rồi đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.72,0:22:38.98,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Your hands are all red.}Tay đỏ chót kìa.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.99,0:22:41.28,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{You're right.}Phải nhỉ.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.28,0:22:42.63,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Allow me.}Xin phép.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.92,0:22:51.21,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{I'll warm some water.}Tôi sẽ chuẩn bị nước nóng.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.93,0:23:00.60,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Y-Young master?!}C-Chủ nhân?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.60,0:23:02.56,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Your hands are freezing, too.}Tay cô cũng lạnh nữa.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.56,0:23:04.89,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{You mustn't, young master.}Không được đâu chủ nhân.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.89,0:23:06.52,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{Y-You'll get cold.}N-Ngài sẽ bị lạnh đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:07.33,0:23:08.49,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{Will I?}Vậy à?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.49,0:23:09.86,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,{You will.}Vâng.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.47,0:23:17.20,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{It's starting to feel warm.}Cảm giác ấm hơn rồi đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.71,0:23:23.97,Main,Lilith,0,0,0,,V-Vào trong thôi, chủ nhân.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.97,0:23:26.16,Main,Yuuri,0,0,0,,{All right, Lilith.}Biết rồi, Lilith.
